ecological_assessment.qualitative_description: The model captures most NPZ model characteristics, but has some deviations from the exact mathematical structure specified

nutrient_equation_uptake.explanation: Partial match. Uses Michaelis-Menten kinetics (N/(K_N+N)), but lacks self-shading term (a/(b+c*P))

nutrient_equation_recycling.explanation: Partial match. Includes nutrient recycling through mortality and grazing, but not with the exact specified mathematical form (beta*lambda*P^2/(mu^2+P^2)*Z)

phytoplankton_equation_growth.explanation: Partial match. Uses nutrient uptake term, but lacks detailed self-shading component

phytoplankton_equation_loss.explanation: Partial match. Includes mortality and predation terms, but not with exact specified mathematical structure

zooplankton_equation.explanation: Close match. Includes predation and mortality terms with similar mathematical structure
